@node "REGISTRATION" "How can I register MAM3?"

===============================================================================

Magic Adreþmanager, the icon, the documentation and examples are (c) Copyright 
1988-95 by Thomas Sch‰fer. All Rights Reserved. This package is Shareware. But 
it's not a limited Demo. It's full featured so you can test it in full action 
for some weeks. But I expect you to register this programm if you like the 
program and want to use regulary or otherwise to stop using it.
The sharewarefee is 20 DM or US$ 20 cash (sorry, but I can't accept cheques).
In return you will get the latest release version of MAM3 on disk. Please allow
max 6 weeks for delivery. Whith this fee you help to ensure continued 
